Description: Port video output from SDL 1.x to SDL 2
 Replace SDL 1.x surface-based rendering with SDL2 window/renderer/texture
 pipeline.  Key changes:
  - SDL_Window + SDL_Renderer + streaming RGB565 SDL_Texture replace the
    SDL_Surface.  Demos write to a plain malloc() pixel_buffer; each frame
    SDL_UpdateTexture() uploads it and SDL_RenderCopy() scales it.
  - SDL_RenderSetLogicalSize() keeps the aspect ratio with black bars; the
    hardware renderer handles the blit internally (no explicit OpenGL FBO
    required; the fallback path falls back to software if the driver does
    not support acceleration).
  - ToggleFullscreen() implemented with SDL_WINDOW_FULLSCREEN_DESKTOP, bound
    to the F key.
  - Window is resizable (SDL_WINDOW_RESIZABLE).
  - Dead GGI/PTC conditional code removed.
  - Build dependency updated: libsdl1.2-dev -> libsdl2-dev.
